[I] A leading threat detection engine

[T] Suricata is the leading independent open source threat detection engine.
[T] By combining intrusion detection (IDS), intrusion prevention (IPS),
[T] network security monitoring (NSM) and PCAP processing, Suricata can
[T] quickly identify, stop, and assess even the most sophisticated attacks.

